                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Problem: Death March Project, Solution: Quite Your Job</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>2</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>2</span>
